  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you see this game first time you might say this game looks easy, but believe me this game hard like it came from hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game you move, you jump sound easy right?</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Beat unnecessary hard levels with capybara.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 - ∞ hours to complete all levels (my friends who tested this game nearly played 10 hours and not even %30 completed of any levels).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With every  level you will face new type of obstacles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you die you will start from begining of level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Currently featuring 4 levels made with love.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3574320/extras/57c11c31c3b6cb34059345237e62e3be.poster.avif?t=1742903487\" width=260 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3574320/extras/57c11c31c3b6cb34059345237e62e3be.webm?t=1742903487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3574320/extras/57c11c31c3b6cb34059345237e62e3be.mp4?t=1742903487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you see this game first time you might say this game looks easy, but believe me this game hard like it came from hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game you move, you jump sound easy right?</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Beat unnecessary hard levels with capybara.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 - ∞ hours to complete all levels (my friends who tested this game nearly played 10 hours and not even %30 completed of any levels).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With every  level you will face new type of obstacles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you die you will start from begining of level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Currently featuring 4 levels made with love.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3574320/extras/57c11c31c3b6cb34059345237e62e3be.poster.avif?t=1742903487\" width=260 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3574320/extras/57c11c31c3b6cb34059345237e62e3be.webm?t=1742903487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3574320/extras/57c11c31c3b6cb34059345237e62e3be.mp4?t=1742903487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
